tableInfo.caption: CRK_LYCK
tableInfo.sql: SELECT A.*,A.ckDm,A.XH,C.MC AS JXMC,A.JH,A.SL,A.XZ,To_char(A.CCRQ,'YYYY-MM-dd') ccrq1,A.RKRQ,D.MC AS JHMC ,A.dwID ,T_JH_ZL.Mc as ZLMC,T_XT_HCLB.MC HCLBMC,T_XT_JLDW.MC JLDW,ADD_MONTHS(A.YFRQ,12*A.YFQX) YFQZ,GLFS,JWH,A.RFID,A.YSID,CASE WHEN QCLB=1 THEN '周转'WHEN QCLB=2 THEN '战备' else '其他'end QCLBMC FROM T_CK_CK A LEFT JOIN T_JH_JX C ON A.JX=C.ID LEFT JOIN T_JH D ON D.ID = A.JH AND D.JX=A.JX left join T_XT_HCLB on T_XT_HCLB.id=A.Hclb left join t_Jh_Zl on T_JH_ZL.id =A.Zl LEFT JOIN T_XT_JLDW ON T_XT_JLDW.ID=D.DW WHERE 1=1 and A.SL>0 order by a.jh,ADD_MONTHS(A.YFRQ,12*A.YFQX),CCRQ1

tableInfo.caption: CRK_LYCK
tableInfo.sql: select T_QX_DW.MC As DRDWMC,T_CK_CRKQD.*,T_CK_DBQD.DCdw,T_CK_DBQD.DRDW,T_CK_DBQD.SQD,T_CK_DBQD.Sl,T_CK_DBQD.DBDH,T_CK_DBQD.DBR, T_JH_ZL.Mc AS ZLMC,T_JH_JX.MC as JXMC,T_CK_DBQD.BBZ,T_XT_BZLB.mc as BZMC,T_XT_HCLB.mc as hclbmc,T_JH.MC JHMC,T_XT_JLDW.MC JLDW,ADD_MONTHS(T_CK_DBQD.YFRQ,12*T_CK_DBQD.YFQX) YFQZ,T_CK_DBQD.Sl KCSL,JJS,ZDDM,SJS from T_CK_CRKQD left join T_CK_DBQD on T_CK_DBQD.Bh =T_CK_CRKQD.Bh and T_CK_DBQD.Jh=T_CK_CRKQD.jh and T_CK_DBQD.Xh=T_CK_DBQD.xh left join T_JH_ZL on T_JH_ZL.ID =T_CK_CRKQD.Zl left join T_JH_JX on T_JH_JX.id = T_CK_CRKQD.JX left join T_QX_DW on T_QX_DW.id=T_CK_DBQD.DRDW left join T_XT_BZLB on T_XT_BZLB.id=T_CK_DBQD.BBZ left join T_XT_HCLB on T_XT_HCLB.id=T_CK_CRKQD.Hclb LEFT JOIN T_JH ON T_JH.ID=T_CK_CRKQD.JH LEFT JOIN T_XT_JLDW ON T_XT_JLDW.ID=T_JH.DW where 1=1

tableInfo.sql: SELECT A.QLDH,A.JX,B.MC JXMC,A.JH,C.MC JHMC,D.MC JLDW,A.SL,E.SPZT from T_HC_QLQD A LEFT JOIN T_JH_JX B ON A.JX=B.ID LEFT JOIN T_JH C ON A.JH=B.ID AND A.JX=C.JX LEFT JOIN T_XT_JLDW D ON C.DW=D.ID LEFT JOIN T_HC_QL E ON A.QLDH=E.QLDH WHERE 1=1 AND E.SPZT=3
